snippet.title: "Dream" Unedited Pre-Alpha Footage
snippet.description:
Following feedback from our Kickstarter campaign here is a 6 minute video of pre-alpha gameplay footage with no commentary or editing.

You can still help us reach our Kickstarter goal here;

http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/samread/dream-0

Any help is greatly appreciated!
